data.description: This property also offers an assumable mortgage of 3.125% with Gateway mortgage. Here is your opportunity to call the Estates section HOME in the highly desired Balcones Creek community.  This home is offered at over 100k below market value,  built-in equity! This stately brick home is the epitome of luxury and style! Nestled on a sprawling .5714-acre lot in the coveted, gated Balcones Creek Estates community located just 10 minutes from HEB and a variety of shops/restaurants in DT Boerne. Built by Perry Homes in 2021, this stunning residence is constructed over a single level offering 3,525 sq ft of living space with 4 en suite bedrooms, a home office, formal dining, and a second living area. The spacious floorplan is well-designed for entertaining, with the formal dining room and eat-in kitchen opening to a large living room featuring a 16' cathedral ceiling, a gas log fireplace, and large-scale windows that offer incredible natural light. The gourmet kitchen astounds with an expansive center island, a breakfast bar, white shaker cabinetry offering amazing storage, classic quartz countertops, undercabinet lighting, and premier stainless-steel appliances including a 5 burner gas cooktop. The primary retreat is tucked away affording great privacy in addition to a vaulted/tray ceiling, a vast walk-in closet, and a luxurious spa bath appointed with separate vanities, walk-in shower with a bench seat, and a deep soaking tub to promote relaxation. The home also hosts three additional bedrooms all with their own private full baths. Enjoy the fresh air in the enormous fenced in backyard, complete with an impressive amount of mature trees and a large covered patio where you can lounge in the shade or grill on a sunny day. The level lot in the back is primed for your future pool/spa. The front entry steps make for great seating to watch those gorgeous Texas sunsets!  Schedule your showing today!
